                                <item xml:id="a2">                 
                                    <locus from="9v" to="10v"/>
                                    <desc type="ProtectivePrayer">                                       
                                        Prayer to arouse love. The text partly is cancelled and partly washed away.
                                    </desc>
                                    <q xml:lang="gez">
                                        <seg part="I">መውደጅ፡ ሽሸ፡ የዩ፡ አይሸምልል፡ <gap reason="ellipsis" resp="bm:GrebTiss1935Codices"/> አቅርባ፡ 
                                            ውስተ<supplied reason="omitted">፡</supplied> ቤተ፡ ከብካብ፡ አስተራክባ፡ በሀገረ፡ እገሌ፡ <gap reason="ellipsis" resp="bm:GrebTiss1935Codices"/>
                                            ከመ፡ ያፈቅር፡ ሐየል፡ ኀበ<supplied reason="omitted">፡</supplied> አንቅዕተ፡ ማያት<supplied reason="omitted">፡</supplied></seg>
                                        <seg part="F">ከመ፡ ማይ፡ ዘታፈልሓ፡ ከማሁ፡ አፍልህ፡ <gap reason="ellipsis" resp="bm:GrebTiss1935Codices"/> ለአመትከ፡ 
                                            <gap reason="ellipsis" resp="bm:GrebTiss1935Codices"/> እግዚአብሔር፡ እገሌ<supplied reason="omitted">፨</supplied></seg>
                                    </q>
                                </item>
                                <item xml:id="a3">                 
